        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Service-Disabled Veterans Small Business Continuation Act</b></p> <p>This bill enables the surviving spouse of a service-disabled veteran who owned a small business to retain priority of the business for a period of time upon the death of the veteran spouse, regardless of the severity of the veteran's disability.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
